### Agent Steering Service — demo requests (VS Code REST Client / JetBrains HTTP)
@base = http://localhost:7071/api

### 1. Start a run (note the returned runId, paste into @run below)
POST {{base}}/runs
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: 11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111

{ "instruction": "summarize the docs", "maxSteps": 10 }

### (set this to the runId from step 1)
@run = PASTE_RUN_ID_HERE

### 2. Check state + audit trail
GET {{base}}/runs/{{run}}

### 3. Pause
POST {{base}}/runs/{{run}}/steer
Content-Type: application/json

{ "action": "Pause" }

### 4. Redirect while paused (changes the instruction)
POST {{base}}/runs/{{run}}/steer
Content-Type: application/json

{ "action": "Redirect", "newInstruction": "translate the docs instead" }

### 5. Resume
POST {{base}}/runs/{{run}}/steer
Content-Type: application/json

{ "action": "Resume" }

### 6. Kill
POST {{base}}/runs/{{run}}/steer
Content-Type: application/json

{ "action": "Kill" }
